  "detailed_description": "<strong>Crypt of the Serpent King</strong> is a medieval first-person hack'n'slash dungeon crawler with roguelike elements.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore large, randomly generated <strong>dungeons</strong>. <br></li><li> Fight goblins, orcs, skeletons, giant spiders and all sorts of underworld <strong>creatures</strong>.<br></li><li> Wield an array of melee and ranged <strong>weapons</strong>. <br></li><li> Jump over lava pits and spike <strong>traps</strong>. <br></li><li> Level up your character's <strong>abilities</strong>.<br></li><li> Choose between 3 levels of <strong>difficulty</strong>, from casual to hardcore.</li></ul>",
